OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FA doctor charged with sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting 38 patients - including
OL,9,Fchildren - while working at two major
OL,10,FNHS hospitals in the West Midlands has
OL,11,Fappeared in court today.
OL,13,FNathaniel Spencer, 38, from Quinton in
OL,14,FBirmingham, is accused of assaulting
OL,15,Fwomen and children at the Royal Stoke
OL,16,FUniversity Hospital in Stoke-on-Trent
OL,17,Fand Russells Hall Hospital in Dudley,
OL,18,Fbetween 2017 and 2021.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FSpencer spoke only to confirm his name
OL,8,Fand was not required to enter pleas
OL,9,Fduring a 45 minute appearance at Stoke-
OL,10,Fon-Trent Crown Court.
OL,12,FThe charges against Spencer are made
OL,13,Fup of 15 counts of sexual assault, 17
OL,14,Fcounts of assault by penetration, nine
OL,15,Fcounts of sexual assault of a child
OL,16,Funder 13, three counts of assaulting a
OL,17,Fchild under 13 by penetration and one
OL,18,Fcount of attempted assault by
OL,19,Fpenetration.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
