OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FHe was charged in December last year
OL,8,Ffollowing what Staffordshire Police
OL,9,Fdescribed as a "complex investigation"
OL,10,Finto alleged sexual offences.
OL,12,FSpencer, a former resident doctor with
OL,13,FThe Dudley Group NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,14,Fmade his first court appearance at
OL,15,FNorth Staffordshire Justice Centre in
OL,16,FJanuary 2026.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FBen Samples, Deputy Chief Crown
OL,8,FProsecutor for the West Midlands CPS
OL,9,FComplex Casework Unit and Serious
OL,10,FViolence, Organised Crime and
OL,11,FExploitation Unit, said: "We have
OL,12,Fdecided to prosecute Nathaniel Spencer
OL,13,Ffor a number of serious sexual
OL,14,Foffences allegedly carried out against
OL,15,Fpatients while he was working as a
OL,16,Fdoctor ` including assault by
OL,17,Fpenetration and sexual assault against
OL,18,Fa child.
OL,26,@sD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
