OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"Our prosecutors have worked at length
OL,8,Fto support a detailed and complex
OL,9,Finvestigation by Staffordshire Police,
OL,10,Fcarefully reviewing the available
OL,11,Fevidence to establish that there is
OL,12,Fsufficient evidence to bring the case
OL,13,Fto trial and that it is in the public
OL,14,Finterest to pursue criminal
OL,15,Fproceedings."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the University
OL,18,FHospitals of North Midlands trust
OL,19,Fsaid, "UHNM has fully cooperated with
OL,20,Fthe police and relevant authorities
OL,21,Fthroughout their investigation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@MO]{D@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
