PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"We cannot comment on an ongoing
OL,8,Fcriminal process but would like to
OL,9,Freassure the public that the safety
OL,10,Fand well-being of our patients and
OL,11,Ftheir relatives are our highest
OL,12,Fpriority.
OL,14,F"We understand that many will find
OL,15,Fthis news deeply concerning for our
OL,16,Fpatients, staff, and the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity. We would encourage anyone
OL,18,Fwho is concerned about the care they
OL,19,Fhave received at our hospitals to
OL,20,Fcontact our dedicated helpline."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
