CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FSpencer was told he will face trial on
OL,8,Fa date to be fixed and at a location
OL,9,Fthat has yet to be determined.
OL,11,FRenewing Spencer's conditional bail at
OL,12,Fhis Crown Court hearing, the Recorder
OL,13,Fof Stoke-on-Trent, Judge Sally Hancox
OL,14,Ftold the court it was not practical
OL,15,Ffor the trial in the case to take
OL,16,Fplace in the city.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
