PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773695157
OL,3,CBirmingham doctor charged with
OL,4,Cmultiple sexual offences appears in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FAdjourning the case until a further
OL,8,Fpre-trial hearing at the same court
OL,9,Flater this year, the judge said she
OL,10,Fhad spoken with those in charge of the
OL,11,FMidlands court circuit in seeking a
OL,12,Fsuitable location for Spencer's trial.
OL,14,FThe judge told Spencer: "There will be
OL,15,Fa further hearing in this case ` that
OL,16,Fwill not be before Monday May 11th `
OL,17,Fwhen further directions will be set.
OL,26,@vD@YOU
